<NOTE>
@{<E>Oliver Wendell Holmes</E>@} ekjan mAr+kinI kabi. t,nAr ekTA miSTi kabitA Achhe 
<LINK to="http://www.poemhunter.com/poem/the-old-man-dreams">@{<E>"The Old Man Dreams."</E>@}</LINK>
tAr ekTA anubAd karechhi erakam. 
<HEAD1>buRo khokAr swap+na</HEAD1>
<PRE>
AhA, yadi sei nabaY\ouban
AbAr Asita phire!
rAjmukuT ke chAhita takhan
parite palita shire?

bayser bali-kunchan~rekhA
jnAnbrriddher bhAle
bahu bachharer sanchita shekhA
chh,nuRe phele janjAle--

muhUr+tamAjhe neche uThitAm
bAlyer uchchhwAse!
AhA sei sukh, swap+nasamAn,
satyai yadi Ase!

kimAshcharYa sei shubhaxaN!
debatAr dUt dwAre
AsiyA hAsiyA kahila--swapan
satya hatei pAre!

jIrNa e jarA habe itihAs
bArdhakyer iti--
bhebe dyAkh.h kichhu rekhe dite chAs.h?
bhabiSyater smrriti?

mane paRe gela patnIr prem
AhA, priyatamA nArI,
kata baraSer nikaSita hem
tAre ki chhARite pAri!

s+warNa Akhare likhila santa,
madhur hAsyadhAre--
brriddha haibe bAlak kintu
jAyA-samabhibyAhAre!

likhiyA chAhila puna pAne mor--
Ar kichhu chAs.h sAthe?
jarA yAbe yabe rabe nA ko tor
Ar kono kichhu hAte!

nA, nA, chAi baTe, chhele meye kaTi,
oder ki kare chhARi!
o go deb~dUt kari go minati
oder rAkhite pAri?

santa takhan tyajiyA lekhnI
kahila uchchahAse--
tui yadi, bokA,  nije khokA habi
tor khokA kise Ase?

Apan kAnDe hese uThi yei
ghum gela mor TuTe
buRoder tare e kabitA tAi
likhechhi sakAle uThe.
</PRE>
</NOTE>
